name: Nolan Berry
profile_summary: This profile belongs to a 35-year-old, 6'0" tall, straight man based in Los Angeles, California. Originally from Portland, Oregon, he is a White Caucasian, who works in the finance industry as an Investment Analyst. An alumnus of the University of Oregon, he values honesty, responsibility, and compassion. Besides being fluent in English and Spanish, he takes a keen interest in reading, hiking, photography, and yoga. As a practicing Catholic, he also identifies as politically moderate and holds 'graduate' education credentials. He has no children, but he does want children in the future. He has a dog and depends on a healthy, active lifestyle which includes occasional alcohol consumption, while refraining from smoking, marijuana, or drug use. Zuriving as an Aquarius with ENTP as their MBTI personality type, he is currently looking for a woman for a monogamous, long-term relationship.
preferences_summary: The user is seeking a woman aged between 28 and 38 years old. She should be between 5'4" to 6'0" tall and have no children, but want to have them in the future. She must be straight, active in her exercise routines, and open to the idea of occasionally drinking, but should not smoke, use marijuana or drugs. The user is open to dating women of any ethnic background - from Black African descent, East Asian, Hispanic/Latino, Middle Eastern, Native American, Pacific Islander, South Asian, Southeast Asian, to White Caucasian. Politically, women of liberal, moderate, or conservative backgrounds are all acceptable. The user's ideal partner would work in Healthcare, Education, Arts, Environment, or Nonprofits and speak English. Honesty and responsibility should be key values she upholds, and she should also enjoy reading, travel, theatre, art, cooking, or hiking. Finally, a woman possessing either an undergraduate or graduate level of education is preferred.
